    },
    {
      "id": "6402f7f1e600350000b1b5f4",
      "text": "[https://www.nhk.or.jp/politics/articles/lastweek/96369.html 日本の島 数え直しで2倍以上に 最多は長崎 北海道が次ぐ | NHK政治マガジン]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1677916146,
      "updated": 1677916146
    },
    {
      "id": "6402f7f1e600350000b1b5f5",
      "text": ">都道府県ごとの島の数は多い順に",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1677916146,
      "updated": 1677916146
    },
    {
      "id": "6402f7f1e600350000b1b5f6",
      "text": "> ▽[長崎県]で1479",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1677916146,
      "updated": 1677916146
    },
    {
      "id": "6402f7f1e600350000b1b5f7",
      "text": "> ▽[北海道]で1473",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
